Love this type of hentai.  It actually had a plot to it.  simplistic but plausible in certain situations.

This adult anime came out between 2007 and 2008, and (after a while) it was already uncensored by a German company.

The show itself it not bad, per say. Considering the subject matter of "Hey! I just paid off your debt! Become by [censored] slaves!" You can do a hella lot worse.

I'm hoping for the "great and mighty" return of Kitty Media Blaster's English dubbing of adult anime. (It makes no sense that Japan's making so much and we in the US are losing out.) And they're atleast making the effort of being verbally distinct. The shounen lead sounds more "emphasized," one of the ladies has a bit more "sass," and the thug sounds like he's from New Jersey. Because when your dubbing studio's stationed between the York and the Jersey... :)
The heralding of the return of dubbed hentai to the American market and beyond. Good on you, kitty media!

I enjoyed this.  A student tries to aid a teacher and her sister, and when he is turned down due to his teacher's pride he angrily goes behind her back and buys up her debts, then she and her sister become his sex slaves to pay them off.  No annoying mosaics, and no-one gets hurt.  And when the mortgages are paid off, is there a reluctance to stop...?  Needs an English translation of the various tattoos, though.

The description doesn't tell you everything about this. It implies that they serve as willing maids to pay off a debt, but it instead has indentured servitude. Great if you like that kind of thing, but otherwise not a great buy if you're simply looking for actual maid service experience.

The story line and animation quality is typical among low budget H-titles. Not great, but not bad either. However, this is not the problem I have. The one I bought from Amazon is a bootleg copy on a DVD-R disc. And appears to be an unauthorized copy NOT from Kitty (Media Blasters). In the opening, where logos are shown, the Kitty logo screen has been replaced with a logo of a pirate ship and literally says "Bootleg" under it. It is beyond me how they are getting away with this.
I watched it once. I liked it and had no problems receiving it.
It was OK but not what I was hoping it would be.
